# Cloudflare Pages redirects. First-match-wins, static files take precedence.
#
# Routes:
#   /         → static Grug.html (Caveman Editorial landing per the
#               Claude Design handoff)
#   /privacy  → static Privacy.html (two-column doc layout)
#   /terms    → static Terms.html
#   /Grug.html, /Privacy.html, /Terms.html  → served directly as static
#                                              files (no rewrite needed)
#   /signin, /dashboard, /admin, /<anything-else>  → SPA fallback to
#                                                     /index.html where
#                                                     React Router takes over
#
# The React app no longer carries a `/` Splash route — Grug.html owns
# the homepage. Auth-gated routes (/dashboard, /admin) still live in
# the React SPA.

/          /Grug.html       200
/privacy   /Privacy.html    200
/terms     /Terms.html      200
/*         /index.html      200
